Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.01,0:00:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掌上的微風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.84,0:00:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在光芒中一閃一閃地舞動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.55,0:00:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經能用全新的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.53,0:00:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.30,0:00:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘管回憶溢滿心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.04,0:00:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的朝氣絕不認輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.78,0:00:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂在乾掉的淚痕中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.15,0:00:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一扇通往夢想的門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.26,0:01:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果煩惱就無法前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.36,0:01:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.86,0:01:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會以迎接朋友的方式\N溫柔地微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.30,0:01:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.97,0:01:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無意間悲傷雖然湧上心頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.34,0:01:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也會試著與人和好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.88,0:01:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是我們的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.28,0:01:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰況越來越激烈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.58,0:01:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甲子園球場的觀眾席\N已經陷入一片瘋狂興奮狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.42,0:02:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前八強的第二場\N崎山高中對長谷高中的比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.52,0:02:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,延長到第11局結束\N依然是一比一平手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.79,0:02:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過接下來輪到本大賽\N首屈一指的強棒,清山上場打擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.20,0:02:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,累計打擊率超過五成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.83,0:02:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在清山緩緩地…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.09,0:02:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#11 賢太郎的初戀!\N只要有愛年齡不是問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.13,0:02:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.26,0:02:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,賢太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.00,0:02:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在要去美香家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.27,0:02:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要不要去?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.41,0:02:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.31,0:03:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我．不．去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.21,0:03:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了,既然他說不去\N就不要理他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.58,0:03:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.62,0:03:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好期待喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.92,0:03:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了我家\N我拿好吃的請你們吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.79,0:03:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點快點,快走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.93,0:03:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小小年紀就耍酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.30,0:03:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“我．不．去”\N居然這麼說,你會後悔的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.67,0:03:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.67,0:03:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時候應該跟他們一起去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.17,0:03:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,美香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.38,0:03:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不對啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.74,0:03:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我看見響子的內褲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.35,0:03:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿房租給她的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.02,0:03:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看見她晒在房裡的內褲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.12,0:03:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.59,0:03:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.86,0:03:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是我的記事本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.96,0:03:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這要怪你愛亂丟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.46,0:03:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是巧合,不過我好高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.33,0:03:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺明天一定會有好事發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.33,0:03:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另外,內褲是粉紅色蕾絲邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.17,0:03:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像還繡有玫瑰花的刺繡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.78,0:04:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,你們在吵什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.95,0:04:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.08,0:04:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明明什麼都沒做…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.25,0:04:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你也太不成熟了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.99,0:04:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的\N是賢太郎看了我的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.12,0:04:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.06,0:04:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有…那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.36,0:04:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳看看這個就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.07,0:04:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你要幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.38,0:04:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.15,0:04:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天我要把那小鬼\N連同他的書包一起丟到垃圾桶裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.33,0:04:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽,我去游泳池囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.30,0:04:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下,賢太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.96,0:05:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的暑假作業還沒做完吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.00,0:05:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦死了,回來再寫啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.50,0:05:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這個孩子真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.84,0:05:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要出門嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.84,0:05:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.31,0:05:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.34,0:05:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去車站接郁子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.58,0:05:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪?你不是要去游泳池嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.48,0:05:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係,不去也無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.02,0:05:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,郁子要來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.55,0:05:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.31,0:06:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賢太郎你也來接我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.71,0:06:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,郁子,不可以這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.58,0:06:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嬸嬸,妳好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.83,0:06:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好多灰塵…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.63,0:06:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可稀奇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.83,0:06:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大熱天的在大掃除嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.97,0:06:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天要在這裡上家教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.37,0:06:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說她積了一堆暑假作業沒做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.58,0:06:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才打掃房間做做門面啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.95,0:06:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下請不要偷窺\N也不要跟我們講話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.08,0:07:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是個很容易分心的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.39,0:07:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.02,0:07:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有在聽?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.22,0:07:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.49,0:07:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把這種桃色雜誌丟在這裡好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.36,0:07:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正要收拾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.90,0:07:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.47,0:07:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫你保管吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.04,0:07:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要在小孩子還在的時候\N拿來還我喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.58,0:07:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的觀察力還蠻敏銳的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.25,0:07:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的手法我已經摸得一清二楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.92,0:07:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥,我來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.65,0:07:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,郁子,怎麼沒敲門就進去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.39,0:07:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我太高興了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.99,0:07:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳這麼早就到啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.59,0:07:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.60,0:07:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四谷,你又挖了一個洞…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.63,0:07:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不不,我只是來還\N我跟五代借的書…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.04,0:07:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他亂說的,他亂說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.44,0:07:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.87,0:07:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,豆藏的納豆定食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.78,0:08:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦,我請客\N明天請你吃啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.78,0:08:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有生雞蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.58,0:08:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,加一顆生雞蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.12,0:08:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.32,0:08:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.32,0:08:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.32,0:08:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼麻煩你費心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.63,0:08:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.70,0:08:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,郁子,妳要認真學喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.70,0:08:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.57,0:08:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有回答“好”的時候最認真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.04,0:08:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥,你的房間\N比我想像中的乾淨很多耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.84,0:08:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行,那裡不能打開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.71,0:08:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪?你不是去游泳嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.75,0:08:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也去唸書好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.05,0:08:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.96,0:08:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你窩在這裡做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.79,0:08:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賢太郎說他想唸書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.19,0:08:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是發燒了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.00,0:08:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想跟郁子一起唸書嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.40,0:08:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.07,0:09:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.71,0:09:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這孩子還真下流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.58,0:09:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.21,0:09:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要我幫你去問問看?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.05,0:09:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用啦,我又沒有這個意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.08,0:09:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.85,0:09:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用就不用啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.72,0:09:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.86,0:09:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就隨便你囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.27,0:09:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個房間有女生來過嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.10,0:09:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要一開始就轉移話題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.47,0:09:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有女朋友嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.41,0:09:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有都沒關係吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.34,0:09:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來你沒有女人緣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.91,0:09:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼話!\N我高中時可是很有女人緣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.18,0:09:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也收過女生寫的情書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.12,0:09:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼初吻也是在那時候嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.32,0:09:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊對啊,那是在高二的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.99,0:09:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳有沒有在聽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.63,0:09:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.73,0:10:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賢太郎說想和你們一起唸書…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.87,0:10:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.77,0:10:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不論是賢太郎還是惣一郎\N通通歡迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.18,0:10:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們要認真寫功課喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.29,0:10:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.23,0:10:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳這個卑鄙的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.56,0:10:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,開始寫功課吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.87,0:10:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賢太郎我問你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.07,0:10:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這次在打什麼歪主意?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.54,0:10:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.84,0:10:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賢太郎,你好文靜喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.85,0:10:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.46,0:10:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這小鬼是怎麼回事啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.21,0:11:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好,要把底乘以高…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.21,0:11:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,對喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.72,0:11:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有在寫嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.02,0:11:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.35,0:11:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.79,0:11:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.06,0:11:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嘛啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.66,0:11:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是彆扭的小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.09,0:11:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣女生不會喜歡你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.13,0:11:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?讓他看看不就好了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.90,0:11:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本就沒有寫嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.14,0:11:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.67,0:11:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是腦袋忘記帶來了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.21,0:11:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我記住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.78,0:11:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾一下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.85,0:12:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,能不能問你一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.18,0:12:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.92,0:12:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想去買晚餐的菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.72,0:12:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有特別喜歡吃的\N或者討厭吃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.59,0:12:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了答謝你教郁子寫功課\N今天我請你吃飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.23,0:12:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳…妳要下廚煮給我吃嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.60,0:12:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.54,0:12:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實在太感謝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.15,0:12:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嬸嬸,我也跟妳一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.55,0:12:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,可是妳功課寫完了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.85,0:12:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,已經差不多寫完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.49,0:12:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊\N那麼賢太郎也一起來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.56,0:12:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.37,0:12:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嬸嬸,快點啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.31,0:12:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下,賢太郎呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.81,0:13:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在外面等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.01,0:13:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.25,0:13:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子可以輕鬆地\N被女生們接納
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.32,0:13:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想一起去的話\N你明說不就好了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.22,0:13:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是不行的\N大人的世界是很複雜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.86,0:13:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之,你不想被她討厭是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.16,0:13:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有把那件事\N跟管理員說吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.20,0:13:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪件事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.34,0:13:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.60,0:13:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看到管理員內褲的事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.51,0:13:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底有沒有說?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.81,0:13:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.15,0:13:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這個臭小子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.71,0:13:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡!\N我剛才還給了你五百圓說!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.05,0:13:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我騙你的,我沒有說啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.75,0:13:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騙人\N真的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.95,0:13:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定說了\N我真的沒有說啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.65,0:13:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看我揍扁你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.69,0:13:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹…幹什麼?放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.16,0:13:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放開我,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.63,0:13:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.36,0:13:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.03,0:13:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.73,0:13:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,放開我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.83,0:13:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放開我,放開我啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.80,0:13:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們三個男生在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.64,0:14:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三個男生?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.48,0:14:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,別管他,我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.11,0:14:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.15,0:14:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪?大哥哥不去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.55,0:14:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代上街買菜好像有點…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.29,0:14:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不對?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.16,0:14:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.99,0:14:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我還得整理房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.35,0:14:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然想來,一開始就明說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.95,0:14:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大人世界的事\N你是不會懂的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.09,0:14:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.83,0:14:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.86,0:15:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有特別想吃什麼菜?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.33,0:15:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦,這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.03,0:15:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嬸嬸,那個不錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.70,0:15:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個?\N不曉得五代喜不喜歡吃?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.54,0:15:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定會喜歡的,因為太好吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.14,0:15:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要是管理員親手做的菜\N我什麼都愛吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.78,0:15:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是豬食還是牛飼料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.58,0:15:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要是管理員做的\N什麼都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.31,0:15:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是在誇獎我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.02,0:15:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.69,0:15:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走,我們去看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.60,0:15:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛肩肉500公克,還有牛肝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.17,0:15:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,謝謝,馬上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.57,0:15:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還要買韭菜和大蒜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.97,0:15:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,還要買雞蛋才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.04,0:15:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這道料理好像很恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.48,0:15:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣果然比較有幹勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.75,0:15:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒有為了某人而做菜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.25,0:15:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為…為了某人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.63,0:16:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡右邊,右邊\N快點按按鈕!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.60,0:16:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危險!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.88,0:16:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來輪到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.26,0:16:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賢太郎,你好厲害喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.26,0:16:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在朋友家有玩過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.04,0:16:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害,好厲害…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.65,0:17:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個\N心情好像突然變得很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.65,0:17:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.67,0:17:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,馬上就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.21,0:17:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.14,0:17:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看喔,雞蛋在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.71,0:17:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了,韭菜和牛肝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.72,0:17:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她做得好起勁喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.22,0:17:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼需要我幫忙的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.29,0:17:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行\N男人要坐著等才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.44,0:17:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子,我來幫忙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.74,0:17:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦,惣一郎你去坐著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.11,0:18:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.21,0:18:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有…沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.12,0:18:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作業的進度還好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.19,0:18:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,郁子還不錯\N賢太郎有點落後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.53,0:18:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賢太郎好像很喜歡郁子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.31,0:18:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這麼一回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.11,0:18:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男生有時候會喜歡\N年紀比他大的女生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.98,0:18:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是那個年紀的男生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.16,0:18:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪個年紀都是一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.29,0:18:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.56,0:18:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.63,0:18:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是都流血了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.70,0:18:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫你剛才要說那種話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.01,0:19:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是,真的都是一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.19,0:19:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肚子好餓喔,飯菜煮好了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.92,0:19:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪?你們在做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.79,0:19:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有…沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.77,0:19:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.04,0:19:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.67,0:19:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.41,0:19:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃,真的好好吃喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.75,0:19:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧,我嬸嬸很會做菜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.22,0:19:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好高興,請多吃一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.22,0:19:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然要多吃一點囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.06,0:19:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這些菜都是為我做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.16,0:20:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好吃了\N響子妳好棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.10,0:20:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,如果你喜歡的話\N我每天都做給你吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.07,0:20:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳…妳的意思是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.25,0:20:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小女子不才\N還請多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.42,0:20:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響…響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.09,0:20:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.60,0:20:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有,我只是在想如果每天\N可以吃到這麼好吃的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.87,0:20:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道該有多好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.17,0:20:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥,惣一郎叔叔\N也說過同樣的話唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.47,0:20:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這道菜是叔叔最喜歡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.98,0:20:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嬸嬸,妳想起了叔叔,對不對?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.71,0:20:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,有一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.12,0:20:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我很高興\N五代也喜歡這道菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.72,0:20:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請多吃一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.92,0:21:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.40,0:21:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想親手做這種料理給他吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.93,0:21:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,他?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.84,0:21:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是足球社的一個男生\N雖然是我自己單戀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.87,0:21:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他真的長得好帥喔\N比我大兩歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.62,0:21:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見囉,大哥哥,賢太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.59,0:21:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改天再來玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.69,0:21:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,賢太郎下次也來我家玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.50,0:21:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.76,0:21:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧,不然會太晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.40,0:21:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,那我走了,拜拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.90,0:21:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見,回家路上小心喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.80,0:22:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.80,0:22:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.54,0:22:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,我請你喝果汁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.14,0:22:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,我讓你請
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.82,0:22:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賢太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.09,0:22:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當男生也有很多痛苦的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.14,0:22:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過夢想…\N夢想千萬不能放棄喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.55,0:23:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得我跟你好像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.79,0:23:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,豬頭!誰跟你像啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.12,0:23:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會變成你這種人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.00,0:23:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這個臭小鬼!站住!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.20,0:23:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你是個優柔寡斷的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.24,0:23:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.17,0:23:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次我要跟郁子說\N你到了幾歲還會尿床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.71,0:23:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要!不要說啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.11,0:23:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活該,我一定…一定要告訴她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.15,0:23:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不怕我說內褲的事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.03,0:23:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是個寡婦沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.90,0:23:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想忘記惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.70,0:23:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是五代居然跟女生約會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.47,0:24:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回\N『愛情的危機!你明明說過愛我』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.84,0:24:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不是在吃醋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.64,0:24:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是為什麼會這麼生氣呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.09,0:24:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何妳能如此若無其事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.44,0:24:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光只是眨個眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.38,0:24:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能讓我悸動不已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:43.55,0:24:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使我身陷險境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.86,0:24:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明已經可以相愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:59.33,0:25:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏時機還不成熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:06.70,0:25:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我快要忍受不了\N快要變成了愚蠢的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:19.22,0:25:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是痛苦的折磨
